add table ip ferm
add chain ip ferm INPUT { type filter hook input priority 0; policy accept; }
flush chain ip ferm INPUT
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport { 22, 443 } accept
add rule ip ferm INPUT ip saddr 192.0.2.0/24 accept
add table ip6 ferm
add chain ip6 ferm INPUT { type filter hook input priority 0; policy accept; }
flush chain ip6 ferm INPUT
add rule ip6 ferm INPUT tcp dport { 22, 443 } accept
add rule ip6 ferm INPUT ip6 saddr 2001:db8::/32 accept
